creator: HONK Technologies, Inc
descriptionHtml:
Stuck on the side of the road? Get help quickly with the HONK towing and roadside assistance app!

Select your required service - tow, flat tire, out of gas, dead battery, locked keys in the car, or stuck in a ditch. Order roadside assistance service within a few clicks and the closest available tow truck service provider will arrive at your exact location.

Breakdowns hurt. Getting help is easy with HONK.

❖ 15-30 MINUTE ARRIVAL TIMES, AVAILABLE 24/7
Our network of over 75,000 trucks nationwide arrive quickly. You will be kept in the know with regular updates, the estimated time of arrival, as well as your driver’s name and number.

❖ TRUSTED & RELIABLE PROFESSIONAL SERVICE PROVIDERS
Feel safe and secure knowing that HONK Service Provider Partners are licensed, insured and meet certain safety and quality standards.

❖ NO CASH REQUIRED
Easy payment options available via credit or debit card. It’s easy, you’ll know the cost for all services before you order. No need to talk price with the driver or get hit with any hidden fees.

❖ NO MEMBERSHIP FEES, AFFORDABLE PRICES
No annual membership fees are applied. Pay only when you order services. Prices vary depending on the service requested.
descriptionShort: Towing and roadside assistance without the membership

Stuck on the side of the road? Get help quickly with the HONK towing and roadside assistance app!

Select your required service - tow, flat tire, out of gas, dead battery, locked keys in the car, or stuck in a ditch. Order roadside assistance service within a few clicks and the closest available tow truck service provider will arrive at your exact location.

Breakdowns hurt. Getting help is easy with HONK.

❖ 15-30 MINUTE ARRIVAL TIMES, AVAILABLE 24/7
Our network of over 75,000 trucks nationwide arrive quickly. You will be kept in the know with regular updates, the estimated time of arrival, as well as your driver’s name and number.

❖ TRUSTED & RELIABLE PROFESSIONAL SERVICE PROVIDERS
Feel safe and secure knowing that HONK Service Provider Partners are licensed, insured and meet certain safety and quality standards.

❖ NO CASH REQUIRED
Easy payment options available via credit or debit card. It’s easy, you’ll know the cost for all services before you order. No need to talk price with the driver or get hit with any hidden fees.

❖ NO MEMBERSHIP FEES, AFFORDABLE PRICES
No annual membership fees are applied. Pay only when you order services. Prices vary depending on the service requested.
